model.name: Pixel Damier Jogging Pants
model.disambiguatingDescription: Elevated activewear: These jogging pants are refreshed for the season in a playful pixel Damier print, which introduces fresh pastel tones to a timeless graphic signature. Cut from lightweight nylon in a staple sporty Louis Vuitton silhouette complete with elasticated ankles and a practical back pocket. A brass hook fastening adds a refined touch.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Main Material : 100% Polyamide
  • Lining : 53% Polyester, 47% Cotton
  • Ecru, Grey
  • Regular fit
  • Model wears size 36
  • Model measurements : Bust 31'' / 79 cm, Height 5' 9" / 175 cm, Waist 23'' / 59 cm, Hips 34,5'' / 87 cm
  • Made in Italy
  • Do not wash
  • Do not bleach
  • Do not tumble dry
  • Iron at a maximum sole-plate temperature of 110°C
  • Mild professionnal dry cleaning in hydrocarbons
